schema.title: Bigconfig
schema.description: Bigconfig is a yaml-based declarative monitoring as code solution. Data engineers can deploy Bigeye metrics from the command-line for convenient and scalable data quality monitoring.

upper_bound.description: Only valid for constant, relative, and standard deviation metrics

lower_bound.description: Only valid for constant, relative, and standard deviation metrics

reference_point.description: Only valid for relative and standard deviation metrics

bucket_size.description: Only valid for data time window metrics
